    <Description>The Arcane Trickster is a Rogue class Archetype who dabbles in their own kind
of magic to augment their abilities. Arcane Tricksters have modest skill in
Enchantment and Illusion magic, but they can also “steal” spells from other
classes. This archetype also summons a magical Mage Hand to cause mischief,
aid in battle, and disable traps from a distance! </Description>
